<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-15 02:24 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A1999 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r a BC-DNC-RAGE-2takes-LADN     08-15 0851
