   RUSSIA-SUBMARINE (Moscow) _ Bad weather is delaying efforts to
rescue more than 100 sailors trapped aboard a military submarine
that lies crippled beneath the Barents Sea. By Sabrina Tavernise
and Christopher Drew.
</P>
<P>
   (An early version of this story will move by 3 p.m. EDT.)
