<P>
   OIL-PRICES (Undated) _ Crude oil prices rose above $32 a barrel
Tuesday for the first time since the Persian Gulf War in 1990 on
worries about low petroleum inventories in the United States and
frank talk by Venezuela about OPEC's thirst for petrodollars. By
Jonathan Fuerbringer.
</P>
<P>
   CENDANT-AVIS (Undated) _ Cendant is proposing to acquire the
