<P>
   GOLF
</P>
<P>
   GLF-ELS _ Ernie Els. Mr. Second Place. Else had a great chance
to win the 1995 PGA at Riviera, with a three shot lead after 54
holes, and shot a final round 72. He tied for 61st at Valhalla in
1996 so this might not be his favorite course. But Els, more than
most, appears to be getting weary of the Tiger Woods domination.
Els is going for the Not So Grand Slam after finishing runner-up in
the Masters, U.S. and British opens. (Sheeley, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution)
</P>
<P>
   GLF-NORMAN _ Greg Norman in first major since his
</P>
<P>
   surgery. (Dolch, Palm Beach Post)
</P>
