least on life support. For those of you eating at your desks right
now, it will come as no surprise that the lunch hour has been
shrinking for much of the 1990s. Even that most hallowed
institution, the expense-account lunch, is fading. &HT;    Main story followed by two sidebars, including the hottest
places to eat lunch, if you have the time. 
