</P>
<P>
   &LR; 6510 Washington St. (at Mulberry), Yountville; (707) 944-0103. &LR; 
 &LR; Open lunch through dinner daily. &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &UR; _ Bouchon &LR; . Step into a Parisian brasserie at this wine country
restaurant and enjoy items from the raw bar, quiche or a wonderful
