<DOCNO> NYT20000815.0285 </DOCNO>
<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-08-15 19:12 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A2550 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-RATINGS-AD-COLUMN-NYT     08-15 1047
