</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    DEMOCRATS STAGE PLUGGED-IN CONVENTION
 &HT;    Repeating to clear garble.
 &HT;    By ANDREW J. GLASS
 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ An Internet-linked computer for each delegation, a
video chat room on the podium, a digital still photo gallery, and a
battery of a black canvas director's chair, tapping away with one
hand on a laptop while holding a microphone in the other. ``The
only time we halt these interactive sessions is when he have a
really majo
</P>
</TEXT>
