   (CVN5) LOS ANGELES -- Aug. 15, 2000 -- DEM-PROTESTS -- Members
of the Los Angeles Police Department, Mobile Field Force, arrive to
the Staples Center, site of the Democratic National Convention,
Tuesday. On Monday night, hundreds of demonstrators threw rocks and
fired steel balls from slingshots at police, who answered by firing
rubber bullets and beanbags from shotguns. (Monica Almeida/The New
